title: The Over-the-Hill Gang (Western, 1969) Walter Brennan, Edgar Buchanan | Movie

sources.title: The Over-the-Hill Gang (Western, 1969) Walter Brennan, Edgar Buchanan | Movie
sources.description:
They will fight one last battle for justice ! (until the sequel)
In the wild and rollicking Old West town, a spirited young newspaper editor takes on the corrupt "tinhorn" mayor, backed by a trigger-happy sheriff and whiskey-soaked judge.  As his campaign gains traction, the editor is joined by a former Texas Ranger and three formidable straight shooters, igniting a riotous showdown. Filled with charm, wit, and a sprinkle of frontier justice.

Original title:  The Over-the-Hill Gang (1969)
This film is available with English & Spanish audio.  And subtitles in many more language options.

Director: Jean Yarbrough
Writers: Jameson Brewer, Leonard Goldberg 
Executive producer: Aaron Spelling 
Stars: Walter Brennan, Edgar Buchanan, Andy Devine, Jack Elam & Gypsy Rose Lee
Genres: Comedy, Western
